sentences.english: Whatever your feelings, this was not about love and a normal relationship.
sentences.chinese: 無論你如何感受，這和愛情無關且是非正常關係。

sentences.english: Adjustable relief valve, may be caused by non normal operation of hydraulic system.
sentences.chinese: 任意調整溢流閥後，可能會造成液壓系統非正常運轉。

sentences.english: Viewpoint which are about definition of the non-normal integration are given in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 本文就非正常積分的定義提出了一些看法。

sentences.english: "Off-the-wall" Questions, also known as "Wild Card" or "No-Right-Answer" Questions.
sentences.chinese: 非正常的提問，或者叫沒有答案的問題。

sentences.english: When language is that which is not normally used, it can indicate lying.
sentences.chinese: 當談話人使用非正常的言語時，暗示着其在說謊。

sentences.english: At low but not normal levels , adiponectin is nociceptive.

sentences.english: The web server may be trying something malicious.

sentences.english: When it dies it sends a non-normal exit signal to the processes in its link set.
sentences.chinese: 它發出非正常退出信號給和它鏈接在一起的進程。

sentences.english: Product had been stored under non-normal conditions or exposed to moist environment.
sentences.chinese: 產品曾被非正常條件下存儲或暴露在潮溼的環境中。

sentences.english: When the pressure-cooker is decompressed abnormally, the utility model can be used repeatedly without changing component.
sentences.chinese: 當壓力鍋非正常泄壓後，無需更換部件便可重複使用。

sentences.english: One is normal, and all others are considered non-normal.
sentences.chinese: 一種是常態，其他所有狀態都認爲是非正常的。

sentences.english: The scoop-proof door lock with an alarm for notification in an abnormal state.
sentences.chinese: 門鎖防斜插非正常狀態報警提醒。

sentences.english: But in these abnormal times, there are two problems with that approach.
sentences.chinese: 不過，在這種非正常時期，這麼做會有兩個問題。
